  <article class="card">
    <p><strong>Languages:</strong> Python, C/C++, SQL, MATLAB; familiar with Scala, Java</p>
    <p><strong>ML Frameworks:</strong> PyTorch, TensorFlow, Keras</p>
    <p><strong>VLMs & LLMs:</strong> Expert in state-of-the-art VLMs and LLMs; instruction tuning, multimodal fine-tuning for video/content understanding</p>
    <p><strong>Cloud & Big Data:</strong> AWS, Apache Spark, PySpark</p>
    <p><strong>DevOps:</strong> Docker, CI/CD pipelines</p>
  </article>

