  <article class="card">
    <h3>Machine learning techniques for advanced frequency management</h3>
    <p class="muted">U.S. Patent · US20240314371A1</p>
  </article>

  <article class="card">
    <h3>Multimedia scene break detection</h3>
    <p class="muted">U.S. Patent · US20240357217A1</p>
